high_descs: Walk forward up to the kitchen sink
Pick up the spoon from the kitchen sink
Look up at the cabinet above the sink
Open the cabinet above the sink and put the spoon in the wine glass
Pick up the wine glass from inside the cabinet
Move a couple feet right then turn to face the kitchen counter
Put the wine glass down on the kitchen counter
anns.task_desc: Put the wine glass with spoon on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn left, hang a right at the white table and walk to the sink.
Pick up the spoon behind the black mug inside the sink.
Look above the sink to reach the cabinet.
Put the spoon inside the gold cup on the bottom shelf in the cabinet.
Pick up the gold cup with the spoon and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the counter to the left.
Put the cup with the spoon in the middle of the counter near the edge.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a spoon on a counter.

high_descs: Go to the front of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the spoon inside the sink.
Reach up to the cabinet above the sink.
Place the spoon on the top shelf above the brown glass.
Place the spoon in the brown glass and take both out of the cabinet
Reach down slowly and move to the counter on the right of the sink.
Place the brown glass with spoon in it on the counter on the right of the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Put the spoon in the brown glass on the counter.
